38:18.129 --> 38:19.630
Stew's delicious, by the way.

38:21.257 --> 38:25.886
♪ <i>Reveals the tears that was on my face</i>
<i>Yeah ♪</i>

38:32.643 --> 38:34.812
[Ruth] You're gonna break
your fucking knuckles.

38:37.315 --> 38:38.441
What happened?

38:39.984 --> 38:42.611
Something weird's going on up there
with Wyatt and Darlene.

38:43.612 --> 38:44.739
Weird how?

38:45.281 --> 38:46.282
[sniffs]

38:50.619 --> 38:52.371
I think they're fucking each other.

38:57.501 --> 38:59.086
[Bobbie Gentry's "Fancy" playing]

38:59.170 --> 39:01.172
<i>♪ Lord, forgive me for what I do... ♪</i>

39:02.715 --> 39:05.468
What's a four-letter word
for a Mongolian hut?

39:07.887 --> 39:08.888
Yurt.

39:09.430 --> 39:10.473
[Darlene laughs]

39:10.639 --> 39:12.141
[knock on door]

39:25.654 --> 39:26.781
Is he here?

39:27.323 --> 39:29.575
'Cause I'm not leaving
until I talk to him.

39:31.327 --> 39:33.996
Well, you might be standing there
for a long time.

39:34.622 --> 39:35.581
[Wyatt] It's okay.

39:37.375 --> 39:38.334
It's fine.

39:46.300 --> 39:47.927
What are you doing here, Wyatt?

39:49.720 --> 39:50.805
Come home.

39:52.640 --> 39:54.475
You don't have to talk to me.

39:55.393 --> 39:57.436
You don't even gotta see my face.

40:00.147 --> 40:01.565
[sighs]

40:02.441 --> 40:05.861
I've thought about this conversation
a hundred times.

40:07.488 --> 40:08.781
I've rehearsed it.

40:12.785 --> 40:14.036
Rehearsed what?

40:17.915 --> 40:19.375
Are you fucking her?

40:22.545 --> 40:24.213
I'm not coming back, Ruth.

40:24.797 --> 40:26.424
I have a good home here,

40:27.425 --> 40:30.511
a real job on the land, and uh...

40:31.637 --> 40:34.598
I think it might be good if Three came
and stayed here, too.

40:37.143 --> 40:38.727
You don't have to be here.

40:40.521 --> 40:41.689
Why are you doing this?

40:41.772 --> 40:43.899
'Cause I know if it were the other way,

40:43.983 --> 40:45.568
I know you'd do the same.

40:47.111 --> 40:48.279
No, I wouldn't.

40:52.324 --> 40:53.576
'Cause I'm happy now.

40:56.162 --> 40:58.539
And I was miserable.

41:02.251 --> 41:03.878
Are you gonna ruin this?

41:05.045 --> 41:08.257
Are you gonna ruin this for me
like you ruined everything else?

41:09.842 --> 41:11.510
You don't know who this lady is.

41:11.594 --> 41:13.721
-Oh, stop it.
-No, she kills people.

41:13.804 --> 41:14.972
She kills people,

41:15.097 --> 41:18.184
and she buries them on that hill,
and she spikes her own heroin--

41:18.267 --> 41:20.978
And you killed my dad and lied about it.

41:21.061 --> 41:22.313
So, where does that put you?

41:24.023 --> 41:25.649
Are you better than her now?

41:27.234 --> 41:28.152
[Wyatt scoffs]

41:30.946 --> 41:31.906
You...

41:32.656 --> 41:34.033
ruined my life.

41:36.243 --> 41:37.369
Is that simple enough?

41:39.955 --> 41:42.082
I love you. Don't you understand that?

41:42.166 --> 41:43.334
Go home, Ruth.

42:09.610 --> 42:11.111
[engine starts]

42:28.629 --> 42:30.798
<i>-</i>[Helen] <i>Marty.</i>
-Yeah, I'm still here.

42:31.549 --> 42:33.300
<i>I just checked. It's not us.</i>

42:35.970 --> 42:37.680
Then who the fuck is it then?

42:38.138 --> 42:39.932
<i>I don't know, but it's not us.</i>

42:40.349 --> 42:41.642
<i>Where are you exactly?</i>

42:42.601 --> 42:45.688
Uh, I'm out in front of a dollar store,

42:45.771 --> 42:49.316
in a mini-mall,
corner of Hawk Nest and Parkway.

42:49.400 --> 42:50.651
<i>Is there a back door?</i>

42:51.652 --> 42:54.738
Um, there's an alleyway,
so there must be.

42:54.989 --> 42:58.450
<i>Go inside. In five minutes,</i>
<i>Nelson will pick you up and take you home.</i>

43:02.121 --> 43:06.250
[Marty over phone] <i>Uh, okay,</i>
<i>but right now, I'm not living at home.</i>

43:08.627 --> 43:11.505
-[Helen] <i>You are tonight.</i>
-[knock on door]

43:20.431 --> 43:21.599
Is Ben here?

43:25.436 --> 43:26.645
He's downstairs.

43:44.913 --> 43:48.083
[Ruth panting]
I don't care if we can't fuck.

43:48.167 --> 43:50.002
I just want to talk, okay?

43:50.377 --> 43:51.295
Okay.

43:51.378 --> 43:53.380
[soft music plays over radio]

43:56.133 --> 43:57.259
What's going on?

44:03.349 --> 44:04.808
I saw Wyatt today.

44:06.518 --> 44:07.978
Up at the Snell place.

44:10.439 --> 44:11.607
What happened?

44:23.535 --> 44:25.371
I ruined his fucking life.

44:26.246 --> 44:27.206
Hey.

44:28.123 --> 44:30.000
Hey, no, you didn't.

44:31.752 --> 44:34.171
What? How?

44:36.256 --> 44:38.300
[breath trembling] I just...

44:40.219 --> 44:41.470
I just, I...

44:41.679 --> 44:44.014
I-- I-- I fucked it all up.

44:45.599 --> 44:48.185
[sobbing] I-- I might--

44:48.268 --> 44:51.397
I might as well have put him
in that psycho's bed.

44:52.606 --> 44:54.525
Shh. Come here.

44:55.192 --> 44:57.194
Shh.

45:01.657 --> 45:03.659
[sniffling]

45:37.818 --> 45:39.153
[racks round]

45:44.491 --> 45:45.909
What are you doing here?

45:47.035 --> 45:48.203
Helen didn't call?

45:48.954 --> 45:51.290
-No.
-That's great. I'm being followed.

45:52.708 --> 45:53.834
Who's following you?

45:53.917 --> 45:55.836
I don't know,
but I gotta spend the night here.

45:57.045 --> 45:59.673
Well... I'll leave, then.

45:59.757 --> 46:01.759
You can't. Helen's orders.

46:02.384 --> 46:04.803
Wendy, I don't want this
any more than you do.

46:05.012 --> 46:05.929
[Jonah] Dad?

46:07.055 --> 46:08.432
-[Marty] Nobody leaves.
-[Charlotte] Why?

46:12.519 --> 46:14.688
-Can we be in our rooms?
-No.

46:14.772 --> 46:17.399
-No, I want you where I can see you.
-[Charlotte sighs]

46:39.755 --> 46:41.632
Now do you believe it wasn't you?

46:42.883 --> 46:45.511
Shut up. [laughs]

46:52.142 --> 46:56.230
[panting, moans]

47:01.819 --> 47:03.153
I could put my drone up.

47:04.238 --> 47:05.405
No, thank you.

47:05.531 --> 47:07.115
Nelson's got us covered.

47:09.201 --> 47:11.453
-[indistinct clatter]
-Jonah, it's your turn.

47:24.925 --> 47:26.844
If we survive the night,
are we still grounded?

47:27.845 --> 47:29.596
Yes, absolutely.

47:33.141 --> 47:34.852
You know, I forgot to tell you.

47:35.936 --> 47:38.063
We're starting a charitable foundation.

47:38.438 --> 47:40.065
So, maybe you guys could...

47:41.024 --> 47:43.694
think about some of the causes
you'd like to support.

47:44.444 --> 47:45.654
That's a great idea.

47:47.155 --> 47:49.491
You could hide dirty money
as cash donations,

47:49.950 --> 47:52.035
and I guess you'd pay less money on tax,
too.

47:53.036 --> 47:53.912
Right?

47:56.123 --> 47:57.332
It's not for that.

47:58.750 --> 47:59.751
It's real.

48:02.921 --> 48:04.506
There is some good we can do.

48:06.049 --> 48:06.925
[Wendy] Hmm?

48:07.676 --> 48:10.721
Well, I think that
that's a very good idea, Mom. [chuckles]

48:15.017 --> 48:15.851
Go.

48:17.436 --> 48:18.437
I did it.

48:47.549 --> 48:50.177
You think, uh, grounding works?

48:50.928 --> 48:52.179
As a principle?

48:55.766 --> 48:57.351
About as well as prison does.

48:57.809 --> 48:58.977
What do we do?

48:59.227 --> 49:01.229
Are you kidding? We ground them.

49:02.064 --> 49:04.816
Remember in Chicago,
when they were, like, ten and seven,

49:04.900 --> 49:07.653
and they wanted to know what, uh,
murder was?

49:13.575 --> 49:14.618
Vaguely.

49:16.119 --> 49:18.413
And Jonah asked if someone was driving

49:18.497 --> 49:20.999
and they hit somebody who was walking,

49:21.083 --> 49:22.459
was that murder?

49:23.043 --> 49:25.003
And I said, "No, it was manslaughter."

49:25.420 --> 49:29.466
And he kept saying it over and over again.
"Manslaughter, manslaughter."

49:32.135 --> 49:34.137
-Why are you remembering this now?
-[chuckles]

49:34.596 --> 49:36.390
And Charlotte realized it was...

49:36.682 --> 49:38.183
"man's-laughter."

49:38.809 --> 49:40.018
It was funny.

49:41.645 --> 49:43.605
You can't-- You can't sleep out here.

49:44.481 --> 49:46.483
Just come to the bedroom, take the bed.

49:46.566 --> 49:48.902
I'll throw some cushions on the floor.

49:49.486 --> 49:50.570
It's fine.

49:53.615 --> 49:55.450
It's a house made of windows.

50:05.752 --> 50:06.920
I'll sleep in the loft.

50:22.769 --> 50:24.229
[Charlotte] What about the war on drugs?

50:24.312 --> 50:25.981
-[Wendy] Funny.
-[Charlotte snickers]

50:27.733 --> 50:28.859
[Jonah] Or animals?

50:30.527 --> 50:32.070
We could save native birds.

50:32.154 --> 50:33.113
[Wendy] Nice.

50:34.406 --> 50:35.782
There's women's issues.

50:35.949 --> 50:36.992
[Wendy] Mm-hmm.

50:39.244 --> 50:40.120
What'd she say?

50:40.996 --> 50:43.331
[sighs]
Three SUVs left early this morning.

50:43.415 --> 50:44.541
They were going north,

50:44.624 --> 50:46.835
and Helen seems to think
that they're headed to Chicago,

50:46.918 --> 50:48.920
so we're all clear.

50:50.547 --> 50:52.883
So... so that's it?

50:52.966 --> 50:54.092
[Marty] Seems like it.

50:58.430 --> 50:59.639
[Charlotte sighs]

51:05.896 --> 51:09.274
I was tired and fell asleep.
[clears throat]

51:14.821 --> 51:17.491
The drop is still on.
You know where it is?

51:18.575 --> 51:21.495
Uh, yeah. The drive-in, in Branch.

51:21.745 --> 51:23.371
Okay. Do you want some coffee?

51:23.914 --> 51:28.043
[stammers] No, I'm good.
I should probably get going, you know.

51:30.045 --> 51:31.379
[Wendy] I'll take her coffee.

51:36.343 --> 51:37.302
[Charlotte] Hmm.

51:43.934 --> 51:45.060
He's off his meds.

51:59.032 --> 52:02.202
Hey, what's the range on your drone?

52:03.745 --> 52:05.372
Three miles, about.

52:05.455 --> 52:07.165
You wanna take a drive with me?

52:08.667 --> 52:09.918
I'm grounded.

52:11.837 --> 52:12.754
So?

52:30.605 --> 52:32.274
You still have her there?

52:32.941 --> 52:35.694
Yep. She's, like, two miles ahead.

52:35.777 --> 52:37.404
[Ben] They better not fuck with her.

52:41.700 --> 52:42.826
You know,

52:43.994 --> 52:45.328
the two of us...

52:47.956 --> 52:51.042
we should drive cross-country
with the drone.

52:52.961 --> 52:55.380
[laughing]

52:55.463 --> 52:57.841
Lots of crazy-ass people

52:58.383 --> 53:00.051
in every city and town.

53:00.677 --> 53:02.262
-Whoo!
-[laughs]

53:04.931 --> 53:06.266
Maybe next summer?

53:08.935 --> 53:09.853
Yeah.

53:11.980 --> 53:13.231
That'd be awesome.

53:16.735 --> 53:17.903
[Ben] Do you see her?

53:41.259 --> 53:42.385
Fuckers.

53:51.937 --> 53:53.021
[Tommy] Go to the back.

53:58.610 --> 54:01.571
You fuckers gonna make me walk
all the way over there?

54:04.908 --> 54:05.951
Dicks.

54:17.337 --> 54:19.339
[cell phone vibrating]

54:22.509 --> 54:23.510
Oh, come on.

54:24.094 --> 54:25.178
[vibrates]

54:26.054 --> 54:28.431
-Get the fuck out of there.
-I don't have time for this.

54:28.556 --> 54:30.976
Something's fucked up. Run, now!

54:31.059 --> 54:32.811
[tires screeching]

54:33.228 --> 54:35.272
[gunfire]

54:45.448 --> 54:46.908
[Ruth gasps]

55:09.931 --> 55:10.932
[engine starts]

55:12.559 --> 55:14.811
[tires screeching]

55:42.589 --> 55:44.507
[theme music playing]
